data.description: Welcome to your own private sanctuary! Nestled in Beech Creek subdivision on .69 of an acre, this 4 bedroom, 3 1/2 bath home has everything you've been looking for with over 2,8oo sq. ft. to enjoy. You will love the interior! A great room with fireplace, stunning kitchen and eat in area, formal dining room, 1/2 bath and laundry/ mud room off of the kitchen, as well as a large bonus room (4th bedroom) upstairs with a full bathroom and closet. Master suite located on the rear of the home, with dual sinks, stand alone tub, shower, & walk-in closet.  2 additional bedrooms with a hall bathroom. Updated throughout, the backyard overlooks the 16th hole and pond of Beech Creek golf course , near Shaw AFB. New HVAC June '23! 2 car side loading garage.   Just a short drive into Sumter or Columbia.
